Loading and preprocessing

Loads supermarket experiment data from folder

Loads .json settings file

Loads taskslist form .json file

convert_action()

Converts actions written in Czech to english counterparts

convert_name_to_item_code()

Converts existing

convert_rightwrong()

Converts RightWrong written in Czech to english counterparts. Then it converts the column to logical

Getters

get_trial_missing_items()

THIS IS IMPORTANT - There is an error in the results log where the MissingItemsList and Additional ItemsList are mistankingly labeled as the other one. So that is why this is here

get_trial_position(<supermarket>)

Returns position during trial

get_trial_times(<supermarket>)

Returns trial times

get_trial_wanted_items()

Returns list of correct items from a trial

get_pickup_position()

Returns position data for picking up a specific object in given trial

get_finished_trials_indices.supermarket()

Returns indices

has_item_codes()

Checks if the items in the data are coded with codes or with czech names

clear_test_logs()

Clears out all test logs from given folder

Convets action logs to test logs. The outcome is the version 5 of the supermarket data due these files originating in the pre version 5 era
